settings.description: BOO!!! The last level was kinda glitchy, hopefully this one isn't!
Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...
Boom Boom gets his airship redesigned, now with a ton of fire! Make sure not to die! He is waiting for a challenge.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the airship section, and the transition to desert land.
Underground bunker as well as a bolt tower. A bolt tower is a tower that uses bolt platforms. Enjoy.
